<h1 class='article-title'>
<a href='http://mashable.com/2015/05/11/liberia-celebrates-end-of-ebola/'>
Liberia celebrates end of Ebola epidemic, but will 'remain vigilant'</a>
</h1>
</header>
<footer>
<div class='article-byline'><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Megan Specia</span></div>
<time class='article-date' datetime='Mon, 11 May 2015 17:26:03 +0000'>
28 days ago</time>
</footer>
<p class='article-excerpt'>Liberia held a day of celebration on Monday and declared a national holiday to mark the end of the Ebola epidemic in the country. 
</p>
</div>
